=== Installing the required packages ===
1. Install Anaconda either from the website www.anaconda.com or using your package manager.
On Windows, you can use winget to install it:
winget install Anaconda.Anaconda3

2. Then run these commands to install the right packages:

conda create -n raylearn -c pytorch pytorch
conda activate raylearn
conda install scipy numpy matplotlib h5py sympy tqdm imageio pytest flake8 pyopengl
conda install -c conda-forge pyglfw
